{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694310/extras/Logo_small.png?t=1719403172\" /><br><br><i>Survive a multitude of fights and gamemodes in this Hack and Slash Arena ARPG. Play as one (or all!) of the many unique characters, each with their own strength, weaknesses, weapons and abilities. Upgrade, personalize and finetune your characters, overcome different challenges and bossfights to create the most powerful team of gladiators to date!</i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 5 Different playable Gladiators, each with a unique skilltree<br></li><li> 4 Unique weapons per gladiator, each with their own playstyle.<br></li><li> Customize your build with quite literally infinite possibilities using the rune system!<br></li><li> 50+ upgrades for your environments, weapons, affixes, ...</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694310/extras/Store_header_conquer.png?t=1719403172\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694310/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1719403172\" /><br><br>Valor features different arenas, each with their own set of challenges. A change of scene is not just that, but also brings along new enemies and environment-specific obstacles and strategies. Every environment ends in an epic bossfight (classic!) where you'll have to prove your worth and understanding of the game's mechanics. Each challenge will require you to identify the best strategy, characters and weapons to complete it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694310/extras/Store_header_style.png?t=1719403172\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694310/extras/Gif3.gif?t=1719403172\" /><br>In Valor, all skins are earned through achievements. On top of that, you're able to customize your particle effects, further adding to the customization possibilities in the game. Battling in style really reflects your achievements!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694310/extras/Store_header_upgrade.png?t=1719403172\" /><br>As your gladiators level up, you'll be able to dig into their upgrade trees to make the most of their abilities. You'll also unlock various runes with special effects that can be equipped by any of your gladiators. Are you the master of innovation with all the different combinations of runes?<br><br>Also check out our newest upcoming release, Spellsinger Towns!<br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Slayer I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1694310/ee4205ba249181758a27b721fab184b5e992f4ab.jpg"},{"name":"Slayer II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1694310/b41c844862c1593a4b75041c69083352a5610a31.jpg"},{"name":"Slayer III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1694310/1fb502ceefe05752c1984d68340bdec08545cf22.jpg"},{"name":"Slayer IV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1694310/86cda87f1ec186b655c8bbd81be3d5456e2e15e7.jpg"},{"name":"Duelist I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1694310/1bcd03063b96f1c31fa73ac86119646c9efc777d.jpg"},{"name":"Duelist II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1694310/b41c844862c1593a4b75041c69083352a5610a31.jpg"},{"name":"Duelist III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1694310/1fb502ceefe05752c1984d68340bdec08545cf22.jpg"},{"name":"Duelist IV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1694310/963bdaaab9ed380f7d36ac0c958997884f66b915.jpg"},{"name":"Captain I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcomm